11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
13 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 255.10 of Title 62, unless there
14 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
15 A. The Office of Management and Enterprise Services shall
16 develop a form for use by each agency, board, commission, department
17 or other entity organized within the executive branch of state
18 government for use by such governmental entity in identifying
19 prospective vendors for contracts to manage federal funds if such
20 funds management is permissible pursuant to the federal law enabling
21 and transferring such funds for expenditure by the state
22 governmental entity. Each such governmental entity shall complete
23 the form and submit it to the Office of Management and Enterprise
