8 SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
9 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 255.11 of Title 62, unless there
10 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
11 The forms submitted to the Office of Management and Enterprise
12 Servies as required by this act shall also be submitted to the
13 Governor, the Speaker of the Oklahoma House of Representatives, the
14 President Pro Tempore of the Oklahoma State Senate, and the Chairs
15 and Vice-Chairs of the standing committees of both chambers of the
16 Oklahoma Legislature responsible for appropriation and budget
17 matters.
18 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
